{
  "id": "adv_event_2309_01_02",
  "title": "優勝を\n目指して",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cafe-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_02-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "わぁ……ここが『とりのきもち』かぁ～\n事務所の近くにこんな雰囲気のいいお店があったのね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow… So this is “Torinokimochi”~\nI didn’t know there was such a nice place near the office.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 9.7985263824,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 9.9851929347
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_02-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "ハツの塩焼きとヨダレドリが美味しいの\nお酒は……熱燗でいい？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The grilled chicken hearts and the necks are delicious.\nFor drinks… Would you like hot sake?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.9851929347,
      "endTime": 16.1754197757,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 16.3820864995
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_02-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "……あ、ええ、大丈夫",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Ah‚ yes‚ that’s fine.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.3820864995,
      "endTime": 20.032086404100003,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 20.2320864279
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_02-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "どうしたの、そんな呆けた顔をして",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What’s wrong? Why do you look so dazed?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.2320864279,
      "endTime": 23.288889225200002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 23.4822225491
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_02-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "あー、その～……mihoさんと普通に喋ってるのが\n新鮮だなーなんて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ well~… It’s just… It’s refreshing to be able\nto have a casual conversation with you…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.4822225491,
      "endTime": 30.762222568200002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 30.9688890059
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_02-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "……私をなんだと思っているの？\n大将、すみません。ハツの塩焼きと――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…What do you take me for?\nExcuse me‚ boss. Grilled chicken hearts and――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.9688890059,
      "endTime": 38.1264854033,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 39.1763266483
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_02-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "んふ～、美味しい！\nさすがmihoさんオススメのメニューね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mm~‚ delicious!\nThis was definitely the right menu choice‚ miho-san!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.2398184696,
      "endTime": 46.1236507334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 46.3303174573
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_02-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "それにしても……貴方といい、さくらといい……\nスリクスと話そうとするなんて変わってるわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Honestly… You and Sakura…\nit’s strange that you’d try to talk to IIIX.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.3303174573,
      "endTime": 53.5254423696,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_02-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "確かに話し掛け辛い雰囲気はあると思う\nでも、みんな話してみたいと思ってるわよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s true that they seem hard to approach‚\nbut I think everyone wants to try talking to them?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.7387757221,
      "endTime": 61.1259186663,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 61.339251828
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_02-mhk005.m4a",
      "text": "……そういえば、怜にも何度か話し掛けられた\nことがあったわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Now that you mention it‚ Rei has tried to talk to me\na couple of times.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.339251828,
      "endTime": 66.30836615589999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 66.6471656718
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_02-hrk006.m4a",
      "text": "……あの、mihoさん\n怜ちゃんのことで聞きたいことがあって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Um‚ miho-san‚\nthere’s something I wanted to ask you about Rei.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.6471656718,
      "endTime": 71.8290702739,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 72.0357369977
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_02-hrk007.m4a",
      "text": "この間、怜ちゃんと二人で話していたでしょう？\nあの後から、怜ちゃんの様子がちょっと変で……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You were talking with Rei the other day‚ weren’t you?\nRei’s been acting a bit strange since then…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.0357369977,
      "endTime": 79.73988652999999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 79.9465533493
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_02-hrk008.m4a",
      "text": "ずっと何か考え込んでるみたいなんだけど……\n私達には話してくれないの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She seems to have something on her mind…\nbut she won’t talk to us about it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.9465533493,
      "endTime": 85.89442198260001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 86.1077554303
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_02-mhk006.m4a",
      "text": "何を考えてるかと思えば、そういうことね\n貴方達の問題に私を巻き込まないでちょうだい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So that’s what’s been bothering you.\nDon’t drag me into your problems.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.1077554303,
      "endTime": 93.9454427319,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 94.1454428273
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_02-hrk009.m4a",
      "text": "mihoさん、そこをなんとか！\n話してくれるだけでいいの！　一杯奢るから、ね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Come on‚ miho-san‚ please!\nJust tell me what’s going on! I’ll buy you a drink‚ okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.1454428273,
      "endTime": 102.2433568555,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 102.4566900172
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_02-mhk007.m4a",
      "text": "……はぁ、分かったわ\nただし、一杯では足りないから……三杯ね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Sigh‚ fine.\nBut one drink won’t be enough… Make it three.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.4566900172,
      "endTime": 110.4302954592,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6422.606134700004
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_message-01.m4a",
          "delay": 14222.606134700001
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 17089.2728014
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_02-hrk010.m4a",
      "text": "ただいま～……って、ありゃ、みんな寝たのかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m home~… Huh‚ is everyone asleep?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.5036385137,
      "endTime": 119.9166317541,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_02-hrk011.m4a",
      "text": "あら、誰だろう……{user}君？\nなになに……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ who is it… {user}?\nWhat‚ what is this…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.3966429153,
      "endTime": 128.3062572876,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_02-hrk012.m4a",
      "text": "『期間限定の二人組ユニットのみ参加可能なライブ\nバトル大会が再び開催されるので、希望者は連絡を』",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“A live battle tournament where only temporary duo units\ncan participate is being held again. Please contact us if interested.”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.5129238207,
      "endTime": 139.3575948794,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_02-hrk013.m4a",
      "text": "これって、前に沙季ちゃんと千紗ちゃんが\n出場した大会よね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Isn’t this the tournament\nSaki and Chisa participated in?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.5442616224,
      "endTime": 144.3487739324,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_02-hrk014.m4a",
      "text": "……そうだ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…That’s right!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.5354406277,
      "endTime": 147.01272311210002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――翌朝",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――The next morning",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.8127231121,
      "endTime": 148.7793804962,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_02-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "あ、遙子さん。おはようございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ Haruko-san. Good morning.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.6793974082,
      "endTime": 154.1885129134,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2309_01_02-hrk015.m4a",
